(define/contract (min-operations nums1 nums2)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let ([n (length nums1)])
    (if (and (= (list-ref nums1 (- n 1)) (apply max nums1))
             (= (list-ref nums2 (- n 1)) (apply max nums2)))
        0
        (let* ([max1 (apply max nums1)]
               [max2 (apply max nums2)]
               [pos-max1 (for/or ([i (in-range n)]) (if (= (list-ref nums1 i) max1) i #f))]
               [pos-max2 (for/or ([i (in-range n)]) (if (= (list-ref nums2 i) max2) i #f))])
          (cond
            [(and pos-max1 pos-max2)
             (if (= pos-max1 pos-max2) 1 2)]
            [else -1])))))
